  "texts": [
    "To ensure authenticity, genuine reviews were selected from June 2021 to June 2022, prior to the public release of ChatGPT in November 2022.",
    "These raw reviews contained noise such as symbols, usernames, website links, and misleading tags.",
    "Preprocessing included replacing usernames and links with special tokens and expanding common abbreviations (e.g., \"U, \" \"idk, \" and \"omg\") into fully spelled words.",
    "Elements such as spelling errors and repeated punctuation were retained to preserve the expressive nature of user feedback.",
    "AIgenerated reviews were created via ChatGPT 3.5 and ERNIE Bot."
  ],
